sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import { Typography, Box, Paper } from '@mui/material'; const BatteryDetailsPanel = () => { const battery = useSelector((state:any) => state.battery); return ( <> {"Battery Type:- "+ battery.batteryType} {"Floor Dimension"} {battery.batteryFloorWidth + "FT X " + battery.batteryFloorHeight + "FT"} {"Energy"} {battery.batteryEnergy} {"Cost"} {battery.batteryCost} {"Release Date"} {battery.batteryReleaseDate} {/* Add more Typography components or other content as needed */} ); } export default BatteryDetailsPanel;
